      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "If someone turns out down for a job or a date",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "…it might be a sign they weren’t smart enough to choose you.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "If someone fires you for ‘performance reasons’",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "…it may be less a sign of their high expectations, and more a sign they’re simply a terrible boss.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "And if you don’t make the cut, the team, or the board?",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Well, it may be a sign they’re not right for you, as much as you not being right for them.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "Point is, rejection hurts for as long as you will it to.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "_type": "block",
      "style": "normal",
      "children": [
        {
          "_type": "span",
          "text": "But, often, it’s for the best.",
          "marks": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}